	     Mbombela - The driver of a Polo was killed in a head-on collision that took place on Graceland Road in Secunda, Mpumalanga on Friday night. ER24 spokesperson, Russel Meiring, said paramedics arrived at around 23:00 on Friday night, and found the driver, a man believed to be in his 20s, had been killed in a collision with a bakkie. "Unfortunately, there was nothing paramedics could do to save the man and he was declared dead on the scene," he said. Meiring said the driver of the bakkie, a man believed to be in his 40s, had sustained minor injuries and he was transported to Medi-Clinic Highveld for further medical care. He said local authorities were on the scene for further investigations. 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.  